<br>
Running up any hill and then getting Fade off gives you a better chance of gaining some distance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=iumdidar>iumdidar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/22/03 8:55:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26208.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> KEI  (Koadic's Endless Intellect)</span><hr size=1> If you are on a populated blue server get Koadic's Endless Intellect. At lower lvls this will increase your mana pool and regen amazing (expecially since you aren't a twink) This spell can be cast by a lvl 60+ enchanter and is usually offered in Nexus/Plane of knowledge) for donations. I know you wouldn't have much pp but I'm pretty sure (or at least on my server) a few enchanters wouldn't mind lending this for free to a non-twink character.... KEI will make you never run oom hardly at all. at lvl 7 you will be able to root too! I know i couldn't at lvl 7 since it was a mana hog hehe. <br>
KEI lasts 2+ hours and you will lvl alot easier with it<br>
